kpi_info.title: hsCodeUsageRatioMean (hsCodeUsageRatio_0_0)
kpi_info.use: The average HS-PDSCH code usage ratio. The value is calculated from the accumulated number of HS-PDSCH codes of one TTI related to the total number of TTI per sampling period and the maximun number of HS-PDSCH codes per cell. TTIs where HS-PDSCH codes have been transmitted and where no codes i.e. no TTI's have been transmitted shall be considered. There is no difference if the codes are used as QPSK or 16QAM codes. UPDATED: This counter is sampled with 10 second interval.
